格拉巴爾-基塔羅維奇上任不到九個月，[[歐洲移民危機|歐洲移民危機]]開始升級，大批移民進入[[希臘|希臘]]和[[馬其頓|馬其頓]]，穿過[[塞爾維亞|塞爾維亞]]進入[[匈牙利|匈牙利]]，自此匈牙利開始在南部邊境築起圍墻<ref>{{cite web |author=Associated Press in Budapest |url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2015/jul/13/hungary-begins-work-on-border-fence-to-keep-out-migrants |title=Hungary begins work on border fence to keep out migrants | World news |publisher=The Guardian |date= |accessdate=2016-05-01 |archive-date=2019-05-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190507163125/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2015/jul/13/hungary-begins-work-on-border-fence-to-keep-out-migrants |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2015年9月，匈牙利搭好圍墻并關閉和塞維爾亞的邊境后，移民人潮流向克羅埃西亞，超過2.1萬移民進入該國<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.hrt.hr/299500/vijesti/u-hrvatsku-uslo-oko-21000-izbjeglica-maari-ih-prihvacaju-bez-registracije-kopija-1 |title=HRT: U Hrvatsku ušlo oko 21.000 izbjeglica - Mađari ih prihvaćaju bez registracije |language=hr |publisher=Hrt.hr |date=2016-01-05 |accessdate=2016-05-01 |archive-date=2019-04-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190407203546/https://www.hrt.hr/299500/vijesti/u-hrvatsku-uslo-oko-21000-izbjeglica-maari-ih-prihvacaju-bez-registracije-kopija-1 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。到9月19日，人數升至3.9萬名，同時3.2萬移民離開克羅地亞，途徑斯洛維尼亞和匈牙利<ref>{{cite web |author=Hina |url=http://www.jutarnji.hr/stigle-nove-brojke-u-hrvatsku-dosad-stiglo-36-000-izbjeglica---bapska-nas-je-iznenadila--ali-sada-je-situacija-bolja--dolaze-u-grupama-od-70-ak-ljudi-/1423464/ |title=STIGLE NOVE BROJKE U Hrvatsku dosad stiglo 36.000 izbjeglica: 'Bapska nas je iznenadila, ali sada je situacija bolja, dolaze u grupama od 70-ak ljudi' |publisher=Jutarnji.hr |date=2015-09-22 |accessdate=2016-05-01 |archive-date=2016-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305072508/http://www.jutarnji.hr/stigle-nove-brojke-u-hrvatsku-dosad-stiglo-36-000-izbjeglica---bapska-nas-je-iznenadila--ali-sada-je-situacija-bolja--dolaze-u-grupama-od-70-ak-ljudi-/1423464/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。她任命{{le|安卓利亞·海布蘭格|Andrija Hebrang (son)}}擔任難民危機專員<ref>{{cite web |author=Piše: R.I.A., Hina subota, 19.9.2015. 13:47 |url=http://www.index.hr/vijesti/clanak/kolindin-povjerenik-hebrang-vojska-je-trebala-na-granici-tijelima-zaprijeciti-ulazak-izbjeglica/842867.aspx |title=Kolindin povjerenik Hebrang: Vojska je trebala na granici tijelima zapriječiti ulazak izbjeglica - Vijesti |publisher=Index.hr |date=2015-09-19 |accessdate=2016-05-01 |archive-date=2019-04-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190407203658/https://www.index.hr/vijesti/clanak/Kolindin-povjerenik-Hebrang-Vojska-je-trebala-na-granici-tijelima-zaprijeciti-ulazak-izbjeglica/842867.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

由於議會將於9月25日解散<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.vecernji.hr/hrvatska/josip-leko-najavio-mogucnost-raspustanja-sabora-do-25-rujna-1023543 |title=Josip Leko najavio raspuštanje Sabora 25. rujna - Večernji.hr |publisher=Vecernji.hr |date= |accessdate=2016-05-01 |archive-date=2015-12-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151202014312/http://www.vecernji.hr/hrvatska/josip-leko-najavio-mogucnost-raspustanja-sabora-do-25-rujna-1023543 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，格拉巴爾-基塔羅維奇呼籲在2015年11月8日舉行[[2015年克羅埃西亞國會選舉|國會大選]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.vecernji.hr/hrvatska/parlamentarni-izbori-odrzat-ce-se-najkasnije-15-studenoga-1022261 |title=Večernji doznaje: Parlamentarni izbori održat će se najkasnije 15. studenoga - Večernji.hr |publisher=Vecernji.hr |date=2015-01-09 |accessdate=2016-05-01 |archive-date=2015-10-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151007043312/http://www.vecernji.hr/hrvatska/parlamentarni-izbori-odrzat-ce-se-najkasnije-15-studenoga-1022261 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，然而組建政府的談判進行了76天。格拉巴爾-基塔羅維奇先前於2015年12月22日宣佈，如果接下來24小時內沒能和後人總理達成協議，就會要求提前舉行大選，任命無黨派的過渡政府（據報道過渡政府由達米爾·萬德里奇主持），藉機對參與新政府組建談判的政黨施加巨大壓力，尋求解決方案。危機最終在2015年12月23日解除，格拉巴爾-基塔羅維奇授予[[無黨派|無黨派]]克羅埃西亞裔加拿大商人[[蒂霍米爾·奧雷什科維奇|蒂霍米爾·奧雷什科維奇]]組建新政府的30天命令，奧雷什科維奇是總理任命提名時限前僅幾個小時，由[[克羅埃西亞民主聯盟|克羅埃西亞民主聯盟]]和{{le|獨立名單橋|Bridge of Independent Lists}}選出的。

2015年8月24日，身為軍隊總司令的格拉巴爾-基塔羅維奇收到一份希望在[[克羅埃西亞軍事|軍隊]]使用克羅埃西亞法西斯運動[[烏斯塔沙|烏斯塔沙]]的敬禮{{le|為了祖國，時刻準備著|Za dom spremni}}的請願。她立即拒絕了這份請願，稱它“輕浮、不可接受，具挑釁性”<ref>{{cite web |author= |url=http://www.jutarnji.hr/bizarnu-peticiju-potpisao-i-simunic-od-predsjednice-traze-da-predlozi-uvodenje-pozdrava--za-dom-spremni--u-oruzane-snage-/1404536/ |title=BIZARNU PETICIJU POTPISAO I ŠIMUNIĆ Od predsjednice traže da predloži uvođenje pozdrava 'Za dom spremni' u Oružane snage! |website=Jutarnji.hr |date=2015-08-24 |accessdate=2016-02-28 |archive-date=2016-02-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160203083658/http://www.jutarnji.hr/bizarnu-peticiju-potpisao-i-simunic-od-predsjednice-traze-da-predlozi-uvodenje-pozdrava--za-dom-spremni--u-oruzane-snage-/1404536/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。2015年9月29日，在基塔羅維奇的倡議下，[[大西洋理事會|大西洋理事會]]在紐約舉辦亞得裡亞海-波羅的海-黑海領導人非正式高級會議，會議後來達成了[[三海倡議|三海倡議]]<ref>{{cite web |author= |url=http://www.atlanticcouncil.org/events/past-events/adriatic-baltic-back-sea-leaders-meeting |title=Adriatic-Baltic-Black Sea Leaders Meeting |website=atlanticcouncil.org |date=2015-10-29 |accessdate=2017-07-06 |archive-date=2019-04-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190407203523/https://www.atlanticcouncil.org/events/past-events/adriatic-baltic-back-sea-leaders-meeting |dead-url=no }}</ref>。倡議于2016年正式成立，於2016年8月25日到26日在[[克羅埃西亞|克羅埃西亞]][[杜布罗夫尼克|杜布罗夫尼克]]舉行第一屆峰會<ref>{{cite web |author= |url=https://eblnews.com/news/croatia/dubrovnik-forum-adopts-declaration-called-three-seas-initiative-34593 |title=Dubrovnik Forum adopts declaration called "The Three Seas Initiative" |website=eblnews.com |date=2016-08-25 |accessdate=2017-07-06 |archive-date=2017-01-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170116042751/https://eblnews.com/news/croatia/dubrovnik-forum-adopts-declaration-called-three-seas-initiative-34593 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

2016年4月11日，格拉巴爾-基塔羅維奇和[[美國國務院|美國國務院]]猶太人大屠殺問題特使尼古拉斯·迪恩（{{lang|en|Nicolas Dean}}）會面后，表示“[[克羅埃西亞獨立國|克羅埃西亞獨立國]]最不獨立，最不能保護克羅埃西亞人民的利益”。她補充，“[[烏斯塔沙|烏斯塔沙]]是罪惡政權”，“反法西斯主義是{{le|克羅埃西亞憲法|Constitution of Croatia}}的基礎”，“現代的克羅埃西亞政權是在[[克羅埃西亞獨立戰爭|克羅埃西亞獨立戰爭]]的基礎上建立的”<ref>{{cite web |author=Dragan Matić/ CROPIX |url=http://www.jutarnji.hr/vijesti/hrvatska/kolinda-grabar-kitarovic-ndh-je-bila-najmanje-nezavisna-i-najmanje-je-stitila-interese-hrvata-a-ustaski-rezim-bio-je-zlocinacki/3709554/ |title=KOLINDA GRABAR KITAROVIĆ 'NDH je bila najmanje nezavisna i najmanje je štitila interese Hrvata, a ustaški režim bio je zločinački!' -Jutarnji List |publisher=Jutarnji.hr |date=2016-04-11 |accessdate=2017-01-23 |archive-date=2019-04-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190407203545/https://www.jutarnji.hr/vijesti/hrvatska/kolinda-grabar-kitarovic-ndh-je-bila-najmanje-nezavisna-i-najmanje-je-stitila-interese-hrvata-a-ustaski-rezim-bio-je-zlocinacki/3709554/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2016年5月，格拉巴爾-基塔羅維奇受伊朗總統[[哈桑·鲁哈尼|哈桑·鲁哈尼]]邀請出訪[[德黑蘭|德黑蘭]]。魯哈尼呼籲克羅埃西亞擔任伊朗和歐洲關係的門戶<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.tehrantimes.com/news/402653/Rouhani-Croatia-can-be-gateway-to-Iran-s-ties-with-Europe |title=Rouhani: Croatia can be gateway to Iran’s ties with Europe |publisher=Tehran Times |date=2016-05-18 |accessdate=2016-06-11 |archive-date=2019-04-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190407203532/https://www.tehrantimes.com/news/402653/Rouhani-Croatia-can-be-gateway-to-Iran-s-ties-with-Europe |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |author=Wed 18, May |url=http://www.tehrantimes.com/photo/402647/Rouhani-officially-welcomes-Croatian-president |title=Rouhani officially welcomes Croatian president |publisher=Tehran Times |date=2016-05-18 |accessdate=2016-06-11 |archive-date=2019-04-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190407203528/https://www.tehrantimes.com/photo/402647/Rouhani-officially-welcomes-Croatian-president |dead-url=no }}</ref>。兩國總統重審兩國傳統的{{le|克羅埃西亞-伊朗關係|Croatia–Iran relations|良好關係}}，并簽署經濟合作協議<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.vecernji.hr/svijet/potvrdeni-tradicionalno-dobri-i-prijateljski-odnosi-hrvatske-i-irana-1085342 |title=Potvrđeni tradicionalno dobri i prijateljski odnosi Hrvatske i Irana - Večernji.hr |publisher=Vecernji.hr |date=2016-05-18 |accessdate=2016-06-11 |archive-date=2017-04-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170404155513/http://www.vecernji.hr/svijet/potvrdeni-tradicionalno-dobri-i-prijateljski-odnosi-hrvatske-i-irana-1085342 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2016年5月，{{le|新星電視台|Nova TV (Croatia)}}民意調查顯示格拉巴爾-基塔羅維奇支持度為45%，反對度達45%<ref name="dnevnik1">{{cite web |author=Ma.B. |url=http://dnevnik.hr/vijesti/hrvatska/crobarometar-dnevnika-nove-tv-kako-biraci-ocjenjuju-vodece-politicare---438449.html |title=CROBAROMETAR DNEVNIKA NOVE TV Kako birači ocjenjuju vodeće političare? |publisher=Dnevnik.hr |date=2016-05-26 |accessdate=2016-06-11 |archive-date=2019-04-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190407203553/https://dnevnik.hr/vijesti/hrvatska/crobarometar-dnevnika-nove-tv-kako-biraci-ocjenjuju-vodece-politicare---438449.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2016年3月，支持度上升至52%<ref>{{cite web |author=I.D. |url=http://dnevnik.hr/vijesti/hrvatska/crobarometar-predsjednici-pada-potpora-medju-gradjanima---431361.html |title=CROBAROMETAR Predsjednici pada potpora među građanima |publisher=Dnevnik.hr |date=2016-03-27 |accessdate=2016-06-11 |archive-date=2019-04-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190407203611/https://dnevnik.hr/vijesti/hrvatska/crobarometar-predsjednici-pada-potpora-medju-gradjanima---431361.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。儘管如此，她仍憑藉57%的支持度成為最受歡迎的政治家，總理[[蒂霍米爾·奧雷什科維奇|蒂霍米爾·奧雷什科維奇]]55%排第二<ref name="dnevnik1"/>。2016年10月，格拉巴爾-基塔羅維奇正式訪問[[亞塞拜然|亞塞拜然]][[巴庫|巴庫]]，期間重申支持亞塞拜然在[[納戈爾諾-卡拉巴赫衝突|納戈爾諾-卡拉巴赫衝突]]維持領土完整的立場，認為衝突解決方案“必須是和平的和政治上的”<ref>{{cite web| url =http://www.azernews.az/nation/104168.html| title =President: Croatia, Azerbaijan "have very good political relations without outstanding issues"| publisher =Azernews| date =24 October 2016| accessdate =25 October 2016| archive-date =2018-07-08| archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20180708075725/https://www.azernews.az/nation/104168.html| dead-url =no}}</ref> 。

2017年11月，[[斯洛博丹·普拉利亞克|斯洛博丹·普拉利亞克]]在[[海牙國際法庭|海牙國際法庭]]審判上服毒自殺后，格拉巴爾-基塔羅維奇向普拉利亞克的家人致哀，稱他是一位“寧願獻出他的生活而不是生命的漢子，堅信自己並沒有犯下被定罪的罪行”<ref>[https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2017/11/slobodan-praljak-war-criminal-croatian-hero-171130181546531.html "Slobodan Praljak: War criminal or Croatian hero?"] {{Wayback|url=https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2017/11/slobodan-praljak-war-criminal-croatian-hero-171130181546531.html |date=20180708191621 }} on ''Al-Jazeera'', 30 November 2017.</ref>，補充稱“他的行為深深刺痛了克羅埃西亞人民的心靈，使得前南斯拉夫問題國際刑事法庭永遠懷疑其任務的完成度”<ref>{{cite news|url=http://vijesti.hrt.hr/417929/obracanje-javnosti-predsjednice-rh-u-povodu-presude-haskog-suda|title=Predsjednica: Hrvatski narod prvi se odupro velikosrpskoj agresiji braneći svoju opstojnost i opstojnost BiH|trans-title=President: The Croatian people first resisted the Greater Serbia aggression by defending its survival and the survival of BiH|date=30 November 2017|publisher=Croatian Radiotelevision|language=hr|accessdate=30 November 2017|archive-date=2018-07-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180725204541/http://vijesti.hrt.hr/417929/obracanje-javnosti-predsjednice-rh-u-povodu-presude-haskog-suda|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

2018年3月，格拉巴爾-基塔羅維奇被提名為[[布宜諾斯艾利斯|布宜諾斯艾利斯]]榮譽市民。她的頒獎典禮上表示：“二戰後，許多克羅埃西亞人在阿根廷找到自由的空間，在那他們展現了自身的愛國心，表達了他們對克羅埃西亞人及家園自由的正當要求。”由於許多[[烏斯塔沙|烏斯塔沙]]的官員曾在二戰後逃往阿根廷，她的演說被烏斯塔沙的支持者打斷。在新聞稿中，格拉巴爾-基塔羅維奇駁斥對她演講的“惡意打斷”：“令人傷心的是，許多移民的犧牲至今仍未獲得認可，在前南斯拉夫時代，他們不能在自己的國家宣揚愛國主義，渴望自由和克羅埃西亞獨立，卻遭到監禁、起訴和謀害。”克羅埃西亞人移民到阿根廷的浪潮自1848年開始，1918年到1939年持續，1945年到1956年達到高潮，約有2萬人（大多數是政治移民）移居阿根廷<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.index.hr/vijesti/clanak/kolinda-mnogi-su-hrvati-u-argentini-pronasli-slobodu-nakon-drugog-svjetskog-rata/1031774.aspx|title=Kolinda: Mnogi su Hrvati u Argentini pronašli slobodu nakon Drugog svjetskog rata|publisher=|access-date=2018-07-17|archive-date=2019-04-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190407203652/https://www.index.hr/Vijesti/clanak/kolinda-mnogi-su-hrvati-u-argentini-pronasli-slobodu-nakon-drugog-svjetskog-rata/1031774.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.index.hr/vijesti/clanak/bauk-o-kolindinim-izjavama-u-argentini-da-je-to-izjavila-merkel-strpali-bi-je-u-zatvor/1032086.aspx|title=Bauk o Kolindinim izjavama u Argentini: Da je to izjavila Merkel strpali bi je u zatvor|publisher=|access-date=2018-07-17|archive-date=2018-04-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180409082630/http://www.index.hr/Vijesti/clanak/bauk-o-kolindinim-izjavama-u-argentini-da-je-to-izjavila-merkel-strpali-bi-je-u-zatvor/1032086.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.total-croatia-news.com/politics/26628-president-rejects-malicious-interpretations-of-her-speech-in-argentina|title=President Rejects “Malicious Interpretations" of Her Speech in Argentina|publisher=|access-date=2018-07-17|archive-date=2019-04-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190407203524/https://www.total-croatia-news.com/politics/26628-president-rejects-malicious-interpretations-of-her-speech-in-argentina|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 社會政策 ==
=== LGBT議題 ===
儘管反對[[同性婚姻|同性婚姻]]，格拉巴爾-基塔羅維奇仍支持使同性伴侶享有等同於異性已婚夫婦權利的{{le|克羅埃西亞民事結合|Recognition of same-sex unions in Croatia|终身伴侣关系法}}，讚揚這是良好的妥協。她在就職演說中還提到性取向問題，表示如果她的兒子出櫃，她也會支持<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.jutarnji.hr/vijesti/hrvatska/sto-zapravo-zastupamo-cetiri-kandidata-odgovaraju-na-20-teskih-pitanja-jutarnjeg/595510/ |title=ŠTO ZAPRAVO ZASTUPAMO Četiri kandidata odgovaraju na 20 teških pitanja Jutarnjeg -Jutarnji List |publisher=Jutarnji.hr |date=2014-12-24 |accessdate=2017-01-23 |archive-date=2019-04-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190407203553/https://www.jutarnji.hr/vijesti/hrvatska/sto-zapravo-zastupamo-cetiri-kandidata-odgovaraju-na-20-teskih-pitanja-jutarnjeg/595510/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 墮胎 ===
格拉巴爾-基塔羅維奇是{{le|墮胎權運動|Abortion-rights movements}}的支持者<ref>{{cite web |author=Piše: D.H. ponedjeljak, 31.10.2016. 18:39 |url=http://www.index.hr/vijesti/clanak/kolinda-protiv-katolickih-radikala-da-zenama-treba-omoguciti-pobacaj-kao-i-do-sada/929181.aspx |title=Kolinda protiv katoličkih radikala: "Da, ženama treba omogućiti pobačaj kao i do sada" - Vijesti |publisher=Index.hr |date=2016-10-31 |accessdate=2017-01-23 |archive-date=2019-04-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190407203719/https://www.index.hr/Vijesti/clanak/kolinda-protiv-katolickih-radikala-da-zenama-treba-omoguciti-pobacaj-kao-i-do-sada/929181.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>。她認為，禁止墮胎不是解決方案，強調加強防止意外懷孕的教育。她批評立法過程艱難，指出“體制上下必須改革，通過教育和社會措施讓每位女性生下一個孩子且母親和孩子最終獲得方式恰當的照顧<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.slobodnadalmacija.hr/novosti/hrvatska/clanak/id/448313/kolinda-grabar-kitarovic-moj-osobni-stav-o-pobacaju-je-poznat-ali-zabrana-nista-ne-rjesava |title=Kolinda Grabar Kitarović: Moj osobni stav o pobačaju je poznat, ali zabrana ništa ne rješava > Slobodna Dalmacija |publisher=Slobodnadalmacija.hr |date=2016-10-31 |accessdate=2017-01-23 |archive-date=2019-04-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190407203527/https://www.slobodnadalmacija.hr/novosti/hrvatska/clanak/id/448313/kolinda-grabar-kitarovic-moj-osobni-stav-o-pobacaju-je-poznat-ali-zabrana-nista-ne-rjesava |dead-url=no }}</ref>。”

=== 氣候變化 ===
格拉巴爾-基塔羅維奇曾提過氣候變化對環境及全球安全的危害，表達對環保倡議的支持<ref>{{cite web|url=https://eblnews.com/news/croatia/croatian-president-hails-paris-accord-step-toward-environment-friendly-progress-18845|title=Croatian president hails Paris accord as step toward environment-friendly progress|publisher=eblnews.com|date=2016-04-23|accessdate=2017-05-26|archive-date=2019-04-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190408045858/https://eblnews.com/news/croatia/croatian-president-hails-paris-accord-step-toward-environment-friendly-progress-18845|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2016年，她在紐約聯合國總統簽署《[[巴黎協議|巴黎協議]]》<ref>{{cite web|url=http://newsroom.unfccc.int/media/632121/list-of-representatives-to-high-level-signature-ceremony.pdf|title=Paris Agreement|publisher=United Nations|date=2016-04-22|accessdate=2017-05-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170516205241/http://newsroom.unfccc.int/media/632121/list-of-representatives-to-high-level-signature-ceremony.pdf|archive-date=2017-05-16|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。另一次在聯合國演講時，她表示氣候變化是“大規模破壞的強大武器”<ref>{{cite web |url=https://gadebate.un.org/en/71/croatia |title=H.E. Ms. Kolinda Grabar-Kitarović, President |publisher=UN |date=2016-09-21 |accessdate=2017-05-26 |archive-date=2018-11-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181104152422/https://gadebate.un.org/en/71/croatia |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 私生活 ==
格拉巴爾-基塔羅維奇于1996年和{{le|雅科夫·基塔乔维奇|Jakov Kitarović}}結婚，女兒卡塔琳娜（2001年4月23日）是職業[[花樣滑冰|花樣滑冰]]運動員、全國青少年冠軍，兒子叫盧卡（2003年出生）<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.jutarnji.hr/lijepa-kolindina-kcer-briljira-na-ledu-hoce-li-nova-drzavna-prvakinja-katarina-kitarovic-braniti-boje-hrvatske-na-olimpijskim-igrama-/1546038/|title=LIJEPA KOLINDINA KĆI BRILJIRA NA LEDU Hoće li nova državna prvakinja Katarina Kitarović braniti boje Hrvatske na Olimpijskim igrama?|publisher=Jutarnji list|access-date=2018-07-17|archive-date=2016-04-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160425101425/http://www.jutarnji.hr/lijepa-kolindina-kcer-briljira-na-ledu-hoce-li-nova-drzavna-prvakinja-katarina-kitarovic-braniti-boje-hrvatske-na-olimpijskim-igrama-/1546038|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.tportal.hr/vijesti/hrvatska/346896/Suprug-Kolinde-Grabar-Kitarovic-konacno-izasao-iz-sjene.html|title=Suprug Kolinde Grabar Kitarović konačno izašao iz sjene|publisher=tportal.hr|access-date=2018-07-17|archive-date=2015-10-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151003063725/http://www.tportal.hr/vijesti/hrvatska/346896/Suprug-Kolinde-Grabar-Kitarovic-konacno-izasao-iz-sjene.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gloria.hr/kolinda-grabar-kitarovic-moj-suprug-nije-papucar-nego-moderan-muskarac/|title=Moj suprug nije papučar nego moderan muškarac|publisher=Gloria.hr|access-date=2018-07-17|archive-date=2015-06-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150626235341/http://www.gloria.hr/kolinda-grabar-kitarovic-moj-suprug-nije-papucar-nego-moderan-muskarac/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

格拉巴爾-基塔羅維奇是虔誠的[[羅馬天主教|羅馬天主教]]徒，她曾表示會堅守傳統的基督教價值觀<ref>{{cite web|title=KOLINDA ODUŠEVLJAVA: ‘U Međugorju osjećam duboku spiritualnost i nazočnost onoga u što vjerujem!’|url=http://www.dnevno.hr/vjera/iz-zivota-crkve/kolinda-odusevljava-u-medugorju-osjecam-duboku-spiritualnost-i-nazocnost-onoga-u-sto-vjerujem-946372|publisher=Dnevno.hr|date=13 August 2016|access-date=2018-07-17|archive-date=2018-11-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181121104356/https://www.dnevno.hr/vjera/iz-zivota-crkve/kolinda-odusevljava-u-medugorju-osjecam-duboku-spiritualnost-i-nazocnost-onoga-u-sto-vjerujem-946372/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Kolinda sa prijateljima u privatnoj posjeti Međugorju|url=http://www.haber.ba/vijesti/bih/341709-kolinda-sa-prijateljima-u-privatnoj-posjeti-medugorju|publisher=Haber.ba|date=11 August 2016|access-date=2018-07-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180708133112/https://www.haber.ba/vijesti/bih/341709-kolinda-sa-prijateljima-u-privatnoj-posjeti-medugorju|archive-date=2018-07-08|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

在接受{{le|人民電台|Narodni radio}}採訪時，她表示自己最喜歡的歌手是被指控宣揚極端民族主義的克羅埃西亞歌手{{le|馬克·佩爾科維奇|Marko Perković}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.index.hr/vijesti/clanak/kolindina-vip-loza-fasisti-lopovi-ubojice/801382.aspx|title=Kolindina VIP loža: Fašisti, lopovi, ubojice...|publisher=index.hr|access-date=2018-07-17|archive-date=2021-01-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210128073557/https://www.index.hr/vijesti/clanak/Kolindina-VIP-loza-Fasisti-lopovi-ubojice/801382.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.24sata.hr/news/kolinda-otkrila-djeca-su-me-naucila-thompsonove-pjesme-478257|title=Kolinda otkrila: Djeca su me naučila Thompsonove pjesme|publisher=24 sata|access-date=2018-07-17|archive-date=2018-07-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180709215717/https://www.24sata.hr/news/kolinda-otkrila-djeca-su-me-naucila-thompsonove-pjesme-478257|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

她能說一口流利的[[克羅埃西亞語|克羅埃西亞語]]、[[英語|英語]]、[[西班牙語|西班牙語]]和[[葡萄牙語|葡萄牙語]]，略懂[[德語|德語]]、[[法語|法語]]和[[意大利語|意大利語]]<ref name="natobio"/><ref name="cvkolinda"/>。

在俄羅斯舉辦的[[2018年國際足協世界盃|2018年國際足協世界盃]]上，格拉巴爾-基塔羅維奇觀看了準決賽和[[2018年國際足協世界盃決賽|決賽]]。她穿著國旗顏色衣服，為最終取得亞軍的[[克羅埃西亞國家足球隊|國家隊]]助威<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.rt.com/sport/433278-croatia-grabar-kitarovic-modric-world-cup/|title=Emotional Croatian leader Grabar-Kitarovic consoles Modric after World Cup final defeat (PHOTOS)|website=RT International|language=en|access-date=2018-07-16|archive-date=2021-02-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210216081355/https://www.rt.com/sport/433278-croatia-grabar-kitarovic-modric-world-cup/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。分析公司Mediatoolkit表示，她“成為了她的國家的世界盃明星”，“25%的決賽報道關注她勝過其他球員”，因為她“自費乘坐經濟艙前往俄羅斯，一般在非VIP看台看球賽”<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.theguardian.com/world/2018/jul/16/croatia-president-kolinda-grabar-kitarovic-world-cup|title=Croatia's real World Cup star? The president in the stands|last=Zagreb|first=Una Hajdari in|date=2018-07-16|website=the Guardian|language=en|access-date=2018-07-16|archive-date=2021-04-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210428225850/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2018/jul/16/croatia-president-kolinda-grabar-kitarovic-world-cup|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

